		<title>Arizona’s water is drying up. That’s not stopping the data center rush.</title>
		<link>https://grist.org/technology/arizona-water-data-centers-semiconducters/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jake Bittle]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 09:45:00 +0000</pubDate>
